estrian)|Frank Carr]] <br> ''[[John Barry (equestrian)|John Barry]]'' <br> ''[[Vernon Padgett]]'' || Did not finish\n|}\n\n==References==\n\n{{reflist}}\n* {{cite web | first = Justin | last = Kubatko | title = Equestrianism at the 1924 Paris Summer Games: Men's Three-Day Event, Team | url = https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/summer/1924/EQU/mens-three-day-event-team.html | work = Olympics at Sports-Reference.com | accessdate = 20 August 2009}}\n* {{cite web|last=Wudarski |first=Pawel |year=1999 |url=http://olympic.w.interia.pl/ |title=Wyniki Igrzysk Olimpijskich |language=pl |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090216130930/http://olympic.w.interia.pl/ |archivedate=16 February 2009 }}\n\n{{Olympic champions \u2013 Equestrian team eventing}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Equestrian at the 1924 Summer Olympics - Team eventing}}\n[[Category:Equestrian at the 1924 Summer Olympics|Eventing team]]\n\n\n{{1924-Olympic-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Equestrian at the Olympics}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=June 2017}}\n{{Infobox Olympic event\n|event = Team eventing\n|games = 1924 Summer\n|image = \n|caption = \n|venue = [[Stade Olympique Yves-du-Manoir]]\n|dates = 21\u201326 July\n|competitors = 40\n|nations = 10\n|longnames = yes\n|gold = [[Antonius Colenbrander]], [[Gerard de Kruijff]], [[Charles Pahud de Mortanges]], [[Adolph van der Voort van Zijp]]\n|goldNOC = NED\n|silver = [[Gustaf Hagelin]], [[Cla\u00ebs K\u00f6nig]], [[Carl Gustaf Lewenhaupt]], [[Torsten Sylvan]]\n|silverNOC = SWE\n|bronze = [[Alessandro Alvisi]], [[Emanuele Beraudo di Pralormo]], [[Tommaso Lequio di Assaba]], [[Alberto Lombardi]]\n|bronzeNOC = ITA\n|prev = [[Equestrian at the 1920 Summer Olympics \u2013 Team eventing|1920]]\n|next = [[Equestrian at the 1928 Summer Olympics \u2013 Team eventing|1928]]\n}}\n{{EquestrianAt1924SummerOlympics}}\n\nOne of the competitions in [[equestrian at the 1924 Summer Olympics]] was the team eventing. The rules only allowed military officers to join the competition. From the results of the [[Equestrian at the 1924 Summer Olympics \u2013 Individual eventing|individual eventing]], a team event was compiled.\n\n==Team event==\nThe results of the first three officers were combined. The Dutch team, consisting of [[Adolph van der Voort van Zijp]], [[Charles Pahud de Mortanges]], [[Gerard de Kruijff]] and [[Antonius Colenbrander]] (whose results did not count) won that competition.<ref>[http://www.sportgeschiedenis.nl/2007/06/24/nederlands-goud-8.aspx Description of the team eventing] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110724170714/http://www.sportgeschiedenis.nl/2007/06/24/nederlands-goud-8.aspx |date=24 July 2011 }} {{in lang|nl}}</ref>\n\n==Results==\n\n<small>The scores of riders in italics (the fourth-best rider on each team as well as non-finishers) were not counted.</small>\n\n{| class=wikitable style=\"text-align:center\"\n! Place || Team || Riders || Score\n|-\n| {{gold1}} ||align=left| {{flagIOCteam|NED|1924 Summer}} ||align=left| [[Adolf van der Voort van Zijp]] <br> [[Charles Pahud de Mortanges]] <br> [[Gerard de Kruijff]] <br> ''[[Antonius Colenbrander]]'' || 5297.5\n|-\n| {{silver2}} ||align=left| {{flagIOCteam|SWE|1924 Summer}} ||align=left| [[Cla\u00ebs K\u00f6nig]] <br> [[Torsten Sylvan]] <br> [[Gustaf Hagelin]] <br> ''[[Carl Gustaf Lewenhaupt]]'' || 4743.5\n|-\n| {{bronze3}} ||align=left| {{flagIOCteam|ITA|1924 Summer}} ||align=left| [[Alberto Lombardi]] <br> [[Alessandro Alvisi]] <br> [[Emanuele Beraudo Di Pralormo]] <br> ''[[Tommaso Lequio di Assaba]]'' || 4512.5\n|-\n| 4 ||align=left| {{flagIOCteam|SUI|1924 Summer}} ||align=left| [[Hans B\u00fchler]] <br> [[Charles Stoffel]] <br> [[Werner Fehr (equestrian)|Werner Fehr]] <br> ''[[Ren\u00e9 de Ribeaupierre]]'' || 4338.5\n|-\n| 5 ||align=left| {{flagIOCteam|BEL|1924 Summer}} ||align=left| [[Baudouin de Braband\u00e8re]] <br> [[Jules Bonvalet]] <br> [[Joseph Fallon]] <br> ''[[L\u00e9on Nossent]]'' || 4233.5\n|-\n| 6 ||align=left| 